
i3 window manager packages (in build order):

  l/libev
  l/yajl
  x/xcb-util-xrm
  xap/dmenu		# optional - rofi is recommended
  xap/rofi
  d/perl-common-sense
  d/perl-Types-Serialiser
  d/perl-Canary-Stability
  d/perl-JSON-XS
  d/perl-AnyEvent
  x/i3-gaps
  l/confuse
  xap/i3status
  xap/i3blocks

System-wide configuration is stored in /etc/i3/ directory.

